  <brief_title>Randomized Multicenter Trial of Prehospital Initiated Facilitated Percutaneous Coronary Intervention (PCI) Versus Primary PCI in ST-segment-Elevation MI (STEMI)</brief_title>
  <acronym>LIPSIA STEMI</acronym>
  <official_title>Randomized, Controlled Multicenter Trial of Prehospital Initiated Facilitated PCI Versus Primary PCI in Patients With STEMI LIPSIA-STEMI Trial</official_title>
