    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Angina pectoris &lt; 3 hours

          -  ST-elevation myocardial infarction

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Active bleeding

          -  Active gastric ulcus

          -  Previous stroke

          -  Uncontrolled hypertension (&gt; 200 mmHg)

          -  Cerebral surgery &lt; 8 weeks

          -  Major surgery &lt; 4 weeks

          -  Malignancy

          -  Treatment with coumarines

          -  Pregnancy
      </textblock>
